Description:
You arrive at a ruined plaza in which countless battles seems to have been fought. The debris of black and white automatons lay scattered all over the place. 

The roads ahead you are unguarded and unattended.

You may discover something useful among the fallen guardians, but time is on the essence.
DescriptionAction: What do you want to do?
